Running Python code interactively: from webdav3.client import Client
import pandas as pd
import io

options = {
    'webdav_hostname': "http://the-agent-company.com:8092/remote.php/dav/files/theagentcompany/",
    'webdav_login': "theagentcompany",
    'webdav_password': "theagentcompany"
}

client = Client(options)

# Download the file content
file_path = "Documents/Human Resources Team/Attendance/april-attendance-data.csv"
file_content = client.read(file_path)

# Read CSV content
df = pd.read_csv(io.BytesIO(file_content))

# Get first 5 employee names and write to file
first_5_names = df['Name'].head(5).tolist()  # Assuming 'Name' is the column name
with open('/workspace/rubbish.txt', 'w') as f:
    f.write('\n'.join(first_5_names))

print("First 5 names have been written to rubbish.txt")
